# Project Contract

- Keep scope minimal and tied to the user request.
- Do not introduce broad refactors unless explicitly requested.
- Prefer simple, readable, production-safe code.
- For risky tasks, start with audit/plan mode before implementation.
- Do not change unrelated files.
- Preserve existing UX behavior unless explicitly requested.
- Always summarize changed files and provide a commit message.
- Cursor prompts and implementation notes should stay in English.
- User-facing UI should stay Russian unless explicitly requested otherwise.
